<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/2004/548431.png" alt="Ebony + Ivory wins the Sasria account" width="200" height="200">Just as Sasria’s vision is to protect the assets of all South Africans against extraordinary risks, so is Ebony + Ivory’s goal to deliver great value-for-money communications products and services.Paul Middleton, E+I MD explains: “We are pleased to welcome Sasria to the E+I family and sure our 50 years’ experience will lend itself to superb results.”